vementioned consistency is the result based on features described\nby LI. If features are described by PD, consistency are 0.009092 dex for\nlog$~T_{eff}$ (124.545075 K for $T_{eff}$), 0.198928 dex for log$~g$, and\n0.206814 dex for [Fe/H].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2015 06:29:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-13"}
