l and\napplies directly to sheared immersed granular media in which pore pressure\nfeedback plays a key role (triggering of avalanches, liquefaction).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2015 12:17:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2015 18:09:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-15"}
